INSERT INTO `productos_2401` VALUES(403, 'Cubreasiento Leather Look ZEGA a medida  para Centauro', 'Original', 'untitled-10000.jpg', '', '', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; ">\r\n	Cubreasiento totalmente a medida con corte original para&nbsp;<strong style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; ">Centauro</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; ">\r\n	El empaque original&nbsp;<strong style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; ">ZEGA</strong>&nbsp;contiene:</p>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; ">\r\n	<li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; ">\r\n		Juego completo de cubreasientos (delanteros y traseros) hechos a medida, con los cortes exactos para su veh&iacute;culo.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; ">\r\n		Butacas delanteras con la marca y logo de su veh&iacute;culo, con la novedosa y &uacute;nica etiqueta en goma&nbsp;<strong style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; ">ZEGA</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; ">\r\n		Asiento trasero con respaldar (con apoyabrazo y apoyacabezas incorporados)&nbsp;y asiento corrido.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; ">\r\n		Dos apoyacabezas delanteros.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; ">\r\n		Intrucciones de Instalaci&oacute;n y limpieza.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; ">\r\n		Bolsa con ganchos para sujetar el&aacute;sticas para la instalaci&oacute;n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; ">\r\n	Cubreasiento f&aacute;cil de instalar, siguiendo las instrucciones que se encuentran incluidas en el empaque.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; ">\r\n	Permite mantener el uso de las funciones de sus butacas ya que los cubreasientos&nbsp;<strong style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; ">ZEGA</strong>&nbsp;son hechos completamente&nbsp; a medida, de esta manera podr&aacute; acceder a la maleta de forma original desde la parte interna de su veh&iacute;culo.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; ">\r\n	<strong style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; ">ZEGA</strong>&nbsp;utiliza materiales de alta calidad lo cual certifica el posicionamiento de dicha marca en Venezuela, los cubreasientos son hechos en tela con un laminado de apariencia a piel lo cual brinda lujo y confort en sus asientos sin contar que posee un &uacute;ltimo microlaminado que no permite que la humedad penetre en su asiento.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; ">\r\n	Proteje su tapiceria original del sucio, del desgaste, de los rayos UV, de derrames accidentales de l&iacute;quido, de las u&ntilde;as&nbsp; y de los molestos pelos de su mascota, sin afectar la apariencia de su veh&iacute;culo.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; ">\r\n	Material totalmente lavable a mano o en lavadora (ciclo delicado) y secado al natural, de igual manera tendr&aacute; una gu&iacute;a r&aacute;pido de lavado y cuidado del cubreasiento.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; ">\r\n	<span style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0); "><strong style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; "><em style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; ">PRODUCTO 100% ORIGINAL ZEGA</em></strong><strong style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; "><em style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; ">&nbsp;</em></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; colo